'''二氫去氧嗎啡'''（'''dihydrodesoxymorphine'''，簡寫'''Desomorphine'''，商標名'''Permonid'''），俗名'''鱷魚'''（'''krokodil'''），是[[嗎啡|嗎啡]]的衍生物，擁有快速而強效的[[鴉片類藥物|類鴉片藥物]]的鎮靜、止痛效果。<ref>{{cite book |first1=Alan F. |last1=Casy |first2=Robert T. |last2=Parfitt |title=Opioid analgesics: chemistry and receptors |url=https://archive.org/details/opioidanalgesics00casy_092 |year=1986 |publisher=Plenum Press |location=New York |page=[https://archive.org/details/opioidanalgesics00casy_092/page/n46 32] |isbn=978-0-306-42130-3}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |pmid=13546093 |year=1958 |last1=Bognar |first1=R |last2=Makleit |first2=S |title=Neue Methode für die Vorbereitung von dihydro-6-desoxymorphine |trans_title=New method for the preparation of dihydro-6-desoxymorphine |language=de |volume=8 |issue=6 |pages=323–5 |journal=Arzneimittel-Forschung}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |pages=260–8 |doi=10.1093/bja/34.4.260 |issue=4 |title=A Review of the Chemical Features Associated with Strong Morphine-Like Activity |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_british-journal-of-anaesthesia_1962-04_34_4/page/260 |year=1962 |last1=Janssen |first1=Paul A. J. |journal=British Journal of Anaesthesia |volume=34 |pmid=14451235}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |pages=1061–3 |doi=10.1021/jm00300a009 |title=Agonists-antagonists derived from desomorphine and metopon |year=1970 |last1=Sargent |first1=Lewis J. |last2=May |first2=Everette L. |journal=Journal of Medicinal Chemistry |volume=13 |issue=6 |pmid=4098039}}</ref> 該藥物在[[1932年|1932年]]首次合成，並在[[1934年|1934年]]取得專利。<ref name=patent>{{cite patent
 | country = US
 | number = 1980972
 | status = patent
 | title = Morphine Derivative and Processes
 | pubdate = 1934-19-07
 | gdate = 1934-13-11
 | inventor = Lyndon Frederick Small
}}</ref>在[[瑞士|瑞士]]，二氫去氧嗎啡以'''Permonid'''<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.oasas.ny.gov/AdMed/FYI/Krokodil.cfm | title = Krokodil | publisher = New York State Office of Alcoholism and Substance Abuse Services | access-date = 2017-01-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140213192814/http://www.oasas.ny.gov/AdMed/FYI/Krokodil.cfm | archive-date = 2014-02-13 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>的商標名販售，當時被描述為嗎啡的優良替代品，相比之下開始作用的時間快速，作用期間短暫，而[[噁心|噁心]]與[[呼吸抑制|呼吸抑制]]等副作用皆較為輕微。在等劑量下的作用強度是嗎啡的8~10倍。<ref name = lifsci>{{cite journal|last=Katselou|first=M|author2=Papoutsis, I |author3=Nikolaou, P |author4=Spiliopoulou, C |author5= Athanaselis, S |title=A "Krokodil" emerges from the murky waters of addiction. Abuse trends of an old drug.|journal=Life Sciences|date=May 2014|volume=102|issue=2|pages=81–87|doi=10.1016/j.lfs.2014.03.008|pmid=24650492}}</ref>

==用途==

===醫學用途===
二氫去氧嗎啡曾經在瑞士與俄羅斯作為舒緩嚴重疼痛的止痛藥出售，當時的商品名為Permonid。<ref name = croc>{{cite journal|last=Gahr|first=M|author2=Freudenmann, RW|author3=Hiemke, C|author4=Gunst, IM|author5=Connemann, BJ|author6=Schönfeldt-Lecuona, C|title=Desomorphine goes "crocodile".|journal=Journal of Addictive Diseases|date=2012|volume=31|issue=4|pages=407–12|doi=10.1080/10550887.2012.735570|pmid=23244560|url=http://www.researchgate.net/publication/233938321_Desomorphine_goes_crocodile|access-date=2017-01-10|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206084216/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/233938321_Desomorphine_Goes_Crocodile|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===娛樂用途===
二氫去氧嗎啡在[[2010年|2010年]]開始重獲國際媒體的注目，當時在俄羅斯非法合成這項藥物的數目遽增，可能是因為它能利用[[可待因|可待因]]來相對簡單的合成出來的關係，而可待因是[[非處方藥|非處方藥]]，在藥局能簡單購入。在[[2003年|2003年]]的西伯利亞，私製的二氫去氧嗎啡第一次被查獲，當時俄羅斯官方正在追查一件重大的海洛因製造及走私案。從那時開始，自製的二氫去氧嗎啡橫掃了俄羅斯及[[獨立國協|前蘇聯加盟國]]等地。<ref name = croc/>

該藥物可用類似從[[偽麻黃鹼|偽麻黃鹼]]製造[[甲基安非他命|甲基安非他命]]的程序合成，而所需的[[可待因|可待因]]及[[碘|碘]]能從藥局所售的非處方箋藥物取得，[[紅磷|磷]]則能從火柴盒上的點火片獲得。<ref>{{cite journal |pages=361–70 |doi=10.1134/S1061934808040096 |title=Chromatographic study of expert and biological samples containing desomorphine |year=2011 |last1=Savchuk |first1=S. A. |last2=Barsegyan |first2=S. S. |last3=Barsegyan |first3=I. B. |last4=Kolesov |first4=G. M. |journal=Journal of Analytical Chemistry |volume=63 |issue=4}}</ref>這樣產出的二氫去氧嗎啡就像類似過程產生的甲基安非他命一樣，被過程中的多種毒性化學物質所污染。俄羅斯口語上的自製二氫去氧嗎啡稱作'''鱷魚'''（Krokodil，{{lang-ru|крокодил}}），可能是藥物前驅物{{tsl|en|α-chlorocodide}}的諧音，或是因為吸食者皮膚的潰爛、類似鱷魚的外表而得名。<ref name = croc/>由於[[海洛因|海洛因]]不易取得，而二氫去氧嗎啡的合成相對簡便，造成該毒品的施用人數持續增加。<ref name = drugpo/>在2012年，俄羅斯當局對於含可待因藥物的販售頒布了新限制，部分打擊了二氫去氧嗎啡在俄羅斯的施用。<ref name="Zheluk A, Quinn C, Meylakhs P 2014 e212">{{cite journal |vauthors=Zheluk A, Quinn C, Meylakhs P | title = Internet Search and Krokodil in the Russian Federation: An Infoveillance Study | journal = Journal of Medical Internet Research | volume = 16 | issue = 9 | pages = e212 | year = 2014 | pmid = 25236385 | pmc =  | doi = 10.2196/jmir.3203 }}</ref>施用該毒品的人數在俄羅斯約有100,000人，在鄰國烏克蘭也有約20,000人。<ref name = drugpo>{{cite journal |vauthors=Grund JP, Latypov A, Harris M | title = Breaking worse: The emergence of krokodil and excessive injuries among people who inject drugs in Eurasia | journal = International Journal of Drug Policy | volume = 24 | issue = 4 | pages = 265–274 | year = 2013 | pmid = 23726898 | pmc =  | doi = 10.1016/j.drugpo.2013.04.007 }}</ref>在[[波蘭|波蘭]]的一例毒品過量死亡案例，據信也與二氫去氧嗎啡的使用有關，並且經過了數位前俄羅斯公民的證實。<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Skowronek R, Celiński R, Chowaniec C | title = "Crocodile" – new dangerous designer drug of abuse from the East | journal = Clinical Toxicology | volume = 50 | issue = 4 | pages = 269 | year = 2012 | pmid = 22385107 | pmc =  | doi = 10.3109/15563650.2012.660574 }}</ref>

==副作用==

===毒性===
非法生產的二氫去氧嗎啡通常使用汽油、火柴、硫酸等便宜材料成，合成後常常未去除合成過程中的大量有毒物質如[[碘|碘]]、[[磷|磷]]等，pH 值甚至常常可以低到 3 左右。直接注射這樣的藥物會直接傷害身體組織，如[[皮膚|皮膚]]、[[血管|血管]]、[[骨頭|骨頭]]、[[肌肉|肌肉]]等，長期施用的人可能面臨截肢的命運。<ref name= lifsci/>使用藥物經常造成施用者感染[[壞死性筋膜炎|壞死性筋膜炎]]，而大規模的組織壞死、感染，也使得該藥物獲得了殭屍藥(flesh-eating drug)的別名，但值得注意的是，該藥物本身並不會造成如此的傷害。<ref name="Desomorphine Krokodil Basics">{{cite web|title=Desomorphine (Krokodil) Basics|url=http://www.erowid.org/chemicals/desomorphine/desomorphine_basics.shtml|publisher=Erowid|accessdate=3 April 2014|archive-date=2020-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201210003736/https://www.erowid.org/chemicals/desomorphine/desomorphine_basics.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>施打毒品常見的副作用包括了[[壞疽|壞疽]]、{{tsl|en|phlebitis|靜脈炎}}、[[血栓|血栓]]、[[肺炎|肺炎]]、[[腦膜炎|腦膜炎]]、[[敗血症|敗血症]]、{{tsl|en|osteomyelitis|骨髓炎}}、肝腎損傷、腦損傷、及[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]感染等。<ref name = drugpo/>施打者若沒有正確將藥物注入靜脈的話，注射處會形成[[膿瘍|膿瘍]]，最終導致該處組織壞死。<ref name= lifsci/>動物試驗表明了相對於嗎啡而言，二氫去氧嗎啡擁有較高的[[毒性|毒性]]，較高的[[鎮痛藥|鎮痛能力]]，同時造成更嚴重的[[抑鬱|抑鬱]]，更積極的[[消化作用|消化作用]]，也抑制了組織的{{tsl|en|Anaerobic respiration|厭氧呼吸作用}}。<ref name=DEA>{{cite web|title=DESOMORPHINE (Dihydrodesoxymorphine; dihydrodesoxymorphine-D; Street Name: Krokodil, Crocodil|url=http://www.deadiversion.usdoj.gov/drug_chem_info/desomorphine.pdf|publisher=Drug Enforcement Administration|accessdate=3 April 2014|archive-date=2019-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190111211605/https://www.deadiversion.usdoj.gov/drug_chem_info/desomorphine.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

